    <section id="content4" class="row home-page-content pt-5">
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="About" class="text-corrections highlists-image">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 ">
                    <h2 class="text-center h2 pop-heading">
                        About App:

                    </h2>
                    <p style="padding:5px;" class="highlights-list">
                        Chef Connect is a web application that connects chefs and customers. It is a platform where chefs can showcase their culinary skills and customers can book a chef to cook for them. The application is designed to provide a seamless experience for both chefs and customers. Chefs can create a profile, upload their recipes, and manage their bookings. Customers can browse through the chef profiles, view their recipes, and book a chef for a private dining experience. Chef Connect aims to bring the luxury of fine dining to the comfort of home.
                    </p>
